[Subtitle "Big Show"]
[Description "You begin each game with two bishops. One moves on light squares, while the other roams on dark squares. Together they are a powerful combo!"]

{Both players start with two bishops placed next to the king and queen.One bishop always stays on light squares, while the other always remains on dark squares. } {[%fen "rnbqkbnr/pppppppp/8/8/8/8/PPPPPPPP/RNBQKBNR w - - 0 1"]} {[%highlight "f1"]} {[%highlight "c1"]} {[%highlight "c8"]} {[%highlight "f8"]}
